Immer (Proxy-based) is used twice in the render pipeline:

```typescript
// In RootReducer (line 149)
const nextSliceState = reducer(previousSliceState, action);
// ^ Immer.produce() inside the slice reducer (Proxy wrapping)

// Later (line 172)
return withSelectorValues(next);

